_aChangeLog.text: Added KZ Colours

Created Easy Bhop (revamp)
Created Medium Bhop (revamp)
Created Hard Bhop (revamp)
Created Pro Bhop (revamp)
Made end platform on drop down larger
Changed all map textures to be less seamless and to hurt the eyes a bit less
All floating text changed to illusionary as to not cause collisions
Removed random kz near HNS Chase
Added music to KZ Colours
Removed death climb in favour of a better winners arena for Drop Down
Nerfed dodge course intro (again)
Changed Cvar settings to improve bhops
Created Easy Climb (revamp)
Created Medium Climb (revamp)
Created Hard Climb (revamp)
Changed climb reset to be filter sensitive (improved checkpoints basically)

Added slight deco in main room around winner box
Added some kzgame sounds for completing different hard modes of games (drop down, trail blazing & ski-ball)

Fixed a black texture on the moving platform in spawn
Made more games be able to be controlled by T (for freedays and stuff)
